For Complex Sender and Simple Sender, regardless of version, an API key must be created on the [API Key Management](https://portal.socketlabs.com/x/smtp-api/key-manager) page in your SocketLabs account. It is important to keep your API key secure because it can be used to modify features for your SocketLabs account.
